layout: post
title: "HD - Daybreak"
date: 2024-12-29 12:00:00 -0000
author: HD
quote: "Daybreak spills"
subject: Haiku in the English-Speaking World (Early 20th century)
permalink: /Haiku in the English-Speaking World (Early 20th century)/HD/HD - Daybreak
---

Daybreak spills
like liquid gold,
a soft embrace
upon the waking world.
Mountains rise
ahead,
majestic and still,
a reminder of our strength,
of resilience and beauty.
Every dew-kissed blade
holds a testament,
a silent prayer
to the sun and sky,
a call to new beginnings,
a promise of today.

- HD
